{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}],"title":"Feeling Badly About Saying No"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","abstract":[{"text":"date: 2016-09-01T00:05:16-05:00","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I’ve been on a kick lately about saying no to things. Apparently I’ve been pushed to my limit and can’t handle anything else so everything is turning into a no. But I still feel like a jerk for saying no and I don’t like feeling like a jerk. I start to apologize for saying no when I really meant it."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/brunow","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he."}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","title":"Brunow"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","kind":"article","title":"2016","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","te